      },
      "date": "2012-09-24 14:39:07.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\n(28 inline comments)\n\nThere are some common style issues in the subtests.\n\nost-pools.sh test_23a() also contains quotacheck codes.\n\nWe need find a way to test the new quota codes, currently it always performs sanity-quota-old.sh. Maybe temporarily comparing the version of 2.3.50 in sanity-quota.sh? After the test passed, we can change the version back to 2.3.51.\n\nPlease add the following test parameter into the commit message:\n\nTest-Parameters: envdefinitions=SLOW=yes testlist=sanity-quota",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 3
    },
